scoringPlays.text: Jason Reese 61 Yd pass from Drew Lock (Tucker McCann Kick)

videos.description: Barry Odom flies onto the field in excitement after South Carolina misses a FG in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Missouri head coach fired up after South Carolina missed FG

videos.description: Drew Lock connects with  Jason Reese  for the games first TD.
videos.headline: Lock hits Reese for Missouri's 1st TD

videos.description: Deebo Samuel responds to Mizzou's TD by taking the ensuing kickoff 97 yards.
videos.headline: Samuel takes kickoff back to the house

videos.description: Freshman Jamyest Williams intercepts Drew Lock's pass in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Williams picks off Lock

videos.description: Deebo Samuel scores his second TD of the night scampering for 25 yards to the end zone.
videos.headline: Samuel scores his 2nd TD of the 2nd quarter

videos.description: South Carolina head coach Will Muschamp sheds some light on the first half of the game.
videos.headline: Muschamp reflects on the first half

videos.description: Jake Bentley hits a wide open Hayden Hurst to widen South Carolina's lead.
videos.headline: Bentley finds Hurst to extend the Gamecock lead

videos.description: Emmanuel Hall fully extends to make the hard catch in the 3rd quarter.
videos.headline: Hall leaps for the sick catch on the sideline

videos.description: Tavon Ross comes up with the big hit on A.J. Turner during the kickoff return.
videos.headline: Ross with huge hit on kickoff return

videos.description: Jonathan Johnson  fumbles the punt as the Gamecock's recover.
videos.headline: South Carolina recovers muffed punt

videos.description: Hayden Hurst pounds his way into the end zone, extending South Carolina's lead in the 4th quarter.
videos.headline: Hurst bullies his way in for six

videos.description: Bryson Allen-Williams picks off Jason Lock and waves goodbye to fans as the Gamecocks dominate.
videos.headline: Allen-Williams intercepts Lock

videos.description: The Gamecock QB breaks down the win over Missouri.
videos.headline: Jake Bentley on South Carolina's big 31-13 win

videos.description: The South Carolina star sheds some light on his performance in the win over the Missouri Tigers.
videos.headline: Deebo Samuel on his stellar 2 TD performance

videos.description: Anish Shroff and Mike Golic Jr. discuss the possibility of South Carolina as the dark horse in  the SEC East.
videos.headline: South Carolina offense key to Gamecocks win over Missouri
